    "patch_code": "public static final Set<Integer> INTERESTING_IDS = IntStream.of(55839, 55845, 55982, 56171).boxed().collect(Collectors.toSet());\n\nprivate boolean interestingId(int id){\n    return INTERESTING_IDS.contains(id);\n}\n\nprotected JavaType _typeFromId(String id, DatabindContext ctxt) throws IOException {\n     int i = Integer.parseInt(id);\n       if (!interestingId(i))\n           throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"Unknow ID\");\n       switch(i){\n         case 55839 : \n            //do something\n             break;\n         case 55845 : \n             //do something\n              break;\n        case 55982 : \n            //do something\n             break;\n        case 56171 :\n             //do something\n               break;\n          default:throw new IllegalArgumentException(\"Unsupported type\");\n       }\n    return tf.constructFromCanonical(id);\n }",
